<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٦٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَلْبِسَكُمْ شِيَعًا}</span> ... يَخْلِطَكُمْ فِرَقًا مُتَنَاحِرَةً.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
